Purpose: Merge multiple Latex bibliography files into one
License: GNU GPL v3
Author: Peng Du

USAGE: merger.pl input1.bib input2.bib output.bib

NOTES: 
(1) duplicates(same reference name, case insensitive) in input1.bib and input2.bib are dealt with first
(2) items in file input2.bib is merged into file input1.bib
(3) duplicated items with the exact same content are automatically dropped  

KNOWN PROBLEM:
duplicates of items without 'title=' needs to be removed manually, such as

@STRING{ACMTOMS = "{ACM} Transactions on Mathematical Software"}

